   "text": "BEATS 12-13 \u00b7 the assumption + the rate\nskeleton: money_math\n\u231cniche_N_mm_assumption\u231f \u231cniche_N_mm_rpm\u231f\nSEE: white cards + the shrug icon card\nVOICE: \"Even if we assume just a 3 dollar RPM\u2026\"\n(RPM = earnings per 1,000 views, from our analysis)",
   "fontSize": 15,
   "fontFamily": 1,
   "textAlign": "center",
   "verticalAlign": "middle",
   "containerId": "8Fc8CCpozsrcm4uo",
   "originalText": "BEATS 12-13 \u00b7 the assumption + the rate\nskeleton: money_math\n\u231cniche_N_mm_assumption\u231f \u231cniche_N_mm_rpm\u231f\nSEE: white cards + the shrug icon card\nVOICE: \"Even if we assume just a 3 dollar RPM\u2026\"\n(RPM = earnings per 1,000 views, from our analysis)",
   "lineHeight": 1.25
