   "text": "BEAT 20 \u00b7 \"it's not a fluke\" \u2014 the format twin\nskeleton: channel_b_proof\n\u231cniche_N_channel_b_chip\u231f then \u231cniche_N_channel_b_page\u231f\nSEE \u2460 their name card (name, handle, subscriber +\nvideo counts ON SCREEN \u2014 voice never reads digits)\n\u2461 their channel page \u2014 a wall of same-style videos\nVOICE: \"There is another channel that makes the\nsame kind of videos \u2014\"",
   "fontSize": 14,
   "fontFamily": 1,
   "textAlign": "center",
   "verticalAlign": "middle",
   "containerId": "3k3q2nzojpdmfym4",
   "originalText": "BEAT 20 \u00b7 \"it's not a fluke\" \u2014 the format twin\nskeleton: channel_b_proof\n\u231cniche_N_channel_b_chip\u231f then \u231cniche_N_channel_b_page\u231f\nSEE \u2460 their name card (name, handle, subscriber +\nvideo counts ON SCREEN \u2014 voice never reads digits)\n\u2461 their channel page \u2014 a wall of same-style videos\nVOICE: \"There is another channel that makes the\nsame kind of videos \u2014\"",
   "lineHeight": 1.25
  },
