   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "The whole script is read ONCE by the AI voice \u2014\nit flows like a person talking. We get back the\nexact moment every word is spoken, then slice\nthe recording per beat at word boundaries.\nSlightly sped up to genre pace (~167 wpm).",
